    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Screwdrivers having a blade that rotates with respect to the handle, as the handle is pushed inward toward the blade; permits a screw to be driven easily and with speed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
